data.description: The Gladesdale lifestyle home plan strikes a pristine balance between innovative convenience and classic luxury. Craft your perfect home office, library, or family entertainment lounge in the cheerful study. The Epicurean kitchen features a presentation island & ample room for food storage & meal prep. Your open floor plan provides a sunlit expanse of enhanced livability and decorative possibilities. Each spare bedroom offers plenty of space for growing minds to shine. Your Extended Owner's Retreat presents a serene retreat from the world that includes a deluxe en suite bathroom and walk-in shower and closet. Experience the benefits of our Brand Promise in this remarkable new home plan. Home located on cul-de-sac home site in the beautiful master planned community of The Woodlands Hills. Come enjoy the serine lifestyle of a 17 acres park that includes a dog park, walking and bike trails, tennis courts, splash pad and even a lazy river.
